ὸς ὑ. . . ἐστι γάλακτος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg030:692a:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PA\">PA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">692a12</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of the stomach, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑ. τροφῆς</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg030:682a:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">682a17</biblScope> </bibl>; of the womb, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg012:722b:14\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ GA\">GA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">722b14</biblScope></bibl>, etc. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n108341.9\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> metaph., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πάσης γενέσεως ὑ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg031:49a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ti.\">Ti.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">49a</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg031:51a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">51a</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀρθρῖτις καὶ ποδάγρα πολλῶν ἄλλων κακῶν ὑποδοχαί εἰσιν</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">substitutes, diversions,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ruf.\">Ruf.</a></author> </bibl> </cit> ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0722.tlg001:45:30:62\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Orib.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">